An open-world fishing game with progress saving enabled. 

Level up your fishing skills, sell your fish, and purchase items and vehicles. 

Roleplay with friends, participate in quests, and compete for the top fisherman spot.

Fill up your collection book with your findings. There is no win condition, just have fun!

Tags: exploration, open world, role playing, simulator

Explore the open world of Outlaw's Haven and make your living inside the town of Freehollow. 

Get a job to earn gold and buy items and weapons to challenge other players. 

Became an Outlaw and cause chaos or clean up the town as a Sheriff. 

This game ends when the timer runs out.

Select from favorite LTM loot pools, set up combat scenarios with the new Bot Grenades, and create your own mode by setting options like gravity and fall damage. Fill your game with up to 15 friends on your own island, or matchmake with default options in a public Battle Lab.

Earn gold by eliminating other players. Visit the Witch Doctor and the Warrior to purchase powerful items and use your gold to upgrade your weapons.

Find all the torches around the map to unleash the power of your team's Volcano God! 

First team to 10000 points wins!
